<plot>Hari (Mohanlal), a welder in a small factory, witnesses a gang-related murder and gets inadvertently involved with the underworld. The murder of a benevolent local boss complicates life in the slum where Hari lives, causing his slow transformation to a life of crime. Decent performances, in an otherwise weak script. Interesting perception of Bombay, which is consistently shown (and romanticized) in Malayalam films as being a hotbed of organized crime activity.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?021232</url></doc>
